## Sapling-based Alignment

The main program which handles alignment is align.cpp

--------------------------------
Running the full aligner
--------------------------------
To build: `make`
To run: ./align <readsfile> <referencefile> <outfile> [optional parameters]
    readsfile should be in FASTQ format
    referencefile should be in FASTA format
    outfile will contain a list of SAM records, one per read with the best alignment.

